39
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:05,840
It depends

40
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,840
if you have the courage.

41
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,080
Why does this incense burn so strongly?

42
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,479
This incense is called
"Snow on the Branch".

43
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,800
It's not only strong,

44
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,879
it can also kill.

45
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,400
Yun Juan,

46
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,280
have you ever thought

47
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:43,000
why you stole money from the warehouse,

48
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:45,280
and why Su Man'er helped delay the time?

49
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:49,840
If this matter

50
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,080
is settled,

51
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,360
they'll spend the money,

52
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:54,879
and it fails, then it's
because your hands weren't clean.

53
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,479
I don't expose you

54
