is willing to accept me.

58
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,879
Has she ever urged Xiao Ye
to give you a title?

59
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,120
Did she ever publicly

60
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,000
acknowledge you as
the Second Master's concubine?

61
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,560
When you were beaten,

62
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:21,680
did she come to visit?

63
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:25,719
They said

64
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,240
in the future,

65
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,520
I will be given an official status.

66
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:31,840
If their lips meet,

67
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,319
you hand over the goods.

68
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:36,639
How could they spend real money

69
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:37,840
on you later?

70
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,759
Yun Juan,

71
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,599
never put your fate

72
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,120
in someone else's hands.

73
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,919
In this world,

74
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,919
all dependable paths

75
